<item>
            <title>[LU-4820] extra memcpy in read path</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4820</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;osd_read_prep() in osd-zfs/ calls into dmu_read() which finds the buffers filled osd_bufs_get_read(). this is not needed and cost us extra memcpy() on all the reads.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
